https://jbhnews.com/measles-hits-new-york-city-infected-traveller-reason/19643/


New York City is in danger as the serious disease enters the city. Recently a traveller, who was infected from the virus visited 3 western New York venues. As per the sources, the traveller was infected with measles which is a viral disease as it spreads by the air with respiratory droplets formed from sneezing or coughing.

